+Function:line                                Scope                        Lock state       Batch    Touches rmap?   Risk
+============================================ ============================ ================ ========= =============== ====
+``madvise_cold_or_pageout_pte_range`` (353)  MADV_COLD / MADV_PAGEOUT     mmap_R + PTL     partial  yes (modify)    **H**
