+``remap_page`` (3564)                        split helper: restore        folio_L+anon     no       yes (modify)    H
+``deferred_split_scan`` (varies)             shrinker: drain split queue  folio_L+anon     n/a      yes (modify)    M
+============================================ ============================ ================ ========= =============== ====
+
+mm/khugepaged.c (collapse)
+--------------------------
+
