+``pagemap_scan_pmd_entry`` (varies)          /proc/PID/pagemap            mmap_R + PTL     no       no (read)       L
+``clear_refs_pte_range`` (varies)            /proc/PID/clear_refs         mmap_R + PTL     no       no (modify)     L
+============================================ ============================ ================ ========= =============== ====
+
