+==========
+
+* ``Documentation/mm/sub-pmd-superpages.rst`` — main framing document
+* ``mm/internal.h`` — ``folio_pte_batch_flags`` API
+* ``mm/page_vma_mapped.c`` — rmap walk infrastructure
